<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Handicrafts Store</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" crossorigin="anonymous" />

  <link crossorigin="anonymous" rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
  
</head>

<body class="d-flex flex-column text-center text-white bg-dark">
  <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
    <header class="mb-auto">
      <div class="container">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Handimaps</a>        
          <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
              
              <% if(!currentUser) { %>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
              </li>
              <% } else { %>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
              </li>
              <% } %>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="flex-grow-1 px-3">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="mt-5">What is Handimaps?</h1> <br>
        <p class="lead">
          HandiMaps is a system that provides a location of stores that sells handicrafts around Bataan. The main goal of this system is to provide a platform that will give convenience to search for places that has handicrafts. Also, to promote the locally made crafts by Batae√±os and bring familiarity to locals and tourists of Bataan. <br> <br>
          HandiMaps is a great way to support the local economy and learn about the culture of Bataan. If you are looking for a unique souvenir or gift, be sure to check out the handicrafts that are available through HandiMaps Bataan.
        </p>
        <a href="/handicrafts" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary font-weight-bold text-white">View Store</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-oBqDVmMz9ATKxIep9tiCxS/Z9fNfEXiDAYTujMAeBAsjFuCZSmKbSSUnQlmh/jp3" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-mQ93GR66B00ZXjt0YO5KlohRA5SY2XofN4zfuZxLkoj1gXtW8ANNCe9d5Y3eG5eD" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
